      • getPredElem

        IGuiNode getPredElem()
              throws PNElementException
        This method returns the predecessor of the arc. If the arc has no predecessor (no "start"), the method returns null.
        Returns:
        The predecessor
        Throws:
        PNElementException - if the value is null

      • getSuccElem

        IGuiNode getSuccElem()
              throws PNElementException
        This method returns the successor of the arc. If the arc has no successor (no "end"), the method returns null.
        Returns:
        The successor
        Throws:
        PNElementException - if the value is null
